'''CEC-One''' was a [[Corellian Engineering Corporation/Legends|CEC]] shipyard in orbit around [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]] it was targeted by the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] in [[Operation Roundabout]], in a hope to disable it for [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] use but keep it operational for later reconstruction work. However, the arrival of a Corellian fleet thwarted the Alliance plan.

